{"tid":1355196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何檢舉翻牆的中國網民？這招幫助他們找到回家的路","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T23:46:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"107076d58bbedf8164086e68a783faf18bbc65a1","tid":1355196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-0&h=30091da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 點擊上方連結進入中央網信辦，點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-1&h=88b57acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接著會有個舉報須知，大概看一下就好 不過看完滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/wUUnmQ-3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FwUUnmQ-3&h=22bcb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n△ 接著點擊「匿名用戶舉報」，舉報平台選擇「客戶端 APP」，將 APP 名稱打上，並將 APP 官方的網址也貼上，最後舉報內容填寫違反使用 VPN 等類似陳述即可，因為最重要的截圖，有越多截圖越好，點擊「請選擇附件」來上傳，最後輸入驗證碼後按下繼續舉報即可。另外，同樣重要的是，請將繁體字通通都轉成簡體字，繁轉簡傳送門也準備好啦～舉報成功後會收到一組查詢碼。"},{"pid":"fb2175dce1bc58a6817724ccd59ae6b00fe177e2","tid":1355196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495e10fd85b2a4a583c5b286eefcb6ac88752c97","tid":1355196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99d9a566827950523c2e559091bb672267f248d","tid":1355196,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"我先唔會上大陸個網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62927d844872db68b5b19e6427d3a51f68ca05d3","tid":1355196,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157fb19577b1744f743b10deb3b85f0faf97caee","tid":1355196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:42:36.000Z","msg":"五大訴求係唔夠架！！起碼七大訴求！！！忘記咗監控燈柱？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351886</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84df403bc0de804944692be6a2b0466426907ce2","tid":1355196,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"匿名但就記哂你部機啲料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}